      *
     CSR         ECLR      ENDSR
      *----------------------------------------------------*
      * EDIT                                               *
      *----------------------------------------------------*
     CSR         #EDIT     BEGSR
      *
     C                     MOVELW9SEL     S1SEL
     C                     MOVEL*BLANK    S1TXT
     C                     SELEC
     C           W9KBN     WHEQ '1'
